  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7934660">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7934660/" class="title-link">纵横之术</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7934660"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/poorcharles/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u132274428-10.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/poorcharles/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">寒舍</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-06-11"
      class="main-meta">2016-06-11 22:29:19</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7934660_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  权谋、纵横、捭阖，在《鬼谷》一书中，化成了对“道”的阐释。“道”也者？一阴一阳是也。 纵横捭阖也不过是对于阴阳的拓展。而就当今社会，我认为此书不可不读。因为人际社交，莫不符合阴阳之道。或松弛有度，或刚硬坚强。 这本书浩如烟海、博大精深，可读一生。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
